*Salon Landing Page
Project Overview
This project is a responsive salon landing page designed to provide a seamless and engaging user experience across various devices. 
The website features a modern design with a focus on showcasing salon services, stylists, and customer transformations.

*Features
Dynamic Navigation Menu: Automatically populates based on page sections for easy navigation.
Smooth Scrolling: Enhances the user experience by providing smooth transitions between sections upon clicking navigation links.
Active Section Highlighting: Visually indicates the currently viewed section in the navigation bar as users scroll through the page.
Responsive Design: Ensures the website is fully functional and visually appealing on desktops, tablets, and smartphones.
*Installation and Setup
No additional installation is required for this project. To set up the project locally:

*Clone the repository to your local machine.
Open index.html in your browser to view the website.
*Usage
Navigate through the website using the top navigation bar to explore different sections.
Enjoy seamless transitions between sections with smooth scrolling functionality.
Responsive design adapts to various screen sizes for optimal viewing on any device.
